{
 "name": "RPlog_Retribution_-_The_Fall_of_Palliata_Station",
 "title": "Retribution: The Fall of Palliata Station",
 "summary": "As the war over Coruscant settles into a cold, drawn-out standoff of probing fighter engagements, the Empire exploits intelligence gathered the previous night to mount a decisive assault. The Broadsword and her escort move against the Republic's Palliata Station, with pilots like Aramis and Wolf engaging across the void. In the fierce exchange, Palliata Station falls -- a costly blow to the New Republic that spurs the bolder counter-strikes of the wider retribution campaign. The log chronicles the pivotal loss of the station amid the battle for the capital.",
